original_title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 18, 2019 Tokyo
overview: Fantastica Mania 2019 was a professional wrestling tour, scripted and co-produced by the Japanese New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW) promotion and the Mexican Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre (CMLL) promotion. The tour started on January 11 and ran until January 21, 2019, with shows taking place in Osaka, Ehime, Kyoto, Gifu, Chiba and Tokyo. At Korakuen Hall.
title: NJPW Presents CMLL Fantastica Mania 2019 - Jan 18, 2019 Tokyo
